        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Now when creating a Form Element, if there is no default decorators are specified, the following code add default decorators\r\n{code}\r\n$this->addDecorator('ViewHelper')\r\n ->addDecorator('Errors')\r\n->addDecorator('Description', array('tag' => 'p', 'class' => 'description'))\r\n->addDecorator('HtmlTag', array(\r\n    'tag' => 'dd',\r\n      'id'  => array('callback' => array(get_class($this), 'resolveElementId'))\r\n))->addDecorator('Label', array('tag' => 'dt'));\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nNeed an option to set default Decorators globally rather than current option, Some thing like a static function to set default decorators."
